maneuvers.narrative: Start out going north on Olde Wadsworth Blvd toward Ralston Rd.
Turn right onto Ralston Rd.
Turn right onto Sheridan Blvd/CO-95.
Turn left to take the I-76 E ramp.
Merge onto I-76 E.
Take the I-270 E exit, EXIT 6, toward Limon.
Merge onto US-36 E.
Stay straight to go onto I-70 E/US-40 E/US-287 S. Continue to follow I-70 E (Portions toll) (Crossing into Kansas).
Merge onto I-670 E via EXIT 421B on the left (Crossing into Missouri).
I-670 E becomes I-70 E (Crossing into Illinois).
Merge onto I-64 E via EXIT 3 toward Louisville.
Merge onto I-57 S toward Louisville/Memphis.
Merge onto I-24 E via EXIT 44 toward Nashville (Passing through Kentucky, then crossing into Tennessee).
Keep left to take I-24 E via EXIT 86 toward Chattanooga/Knoxville/I-40 E (Passing through Georgia, then crossing into Tennessee).
Merge onto I-75 S/I-85 S/GA-403 S/GA-401 S via EXIT 185A toward Atlanta (Crossing into Georgia).
Keep left to take I-75 S/GA-401 S toward Macon/International.
Keep right to take I-475 S/GA-408 S via EXIT 177 toward I-75 S/Valdosta.
Merge onto I-75 S via the exit on the left (Crossing into Florida).
Keep left to take I-75 S toward Naples.
Take the County Hwy-672 exit, EXIT 246, toward Apollo Beach.
Keep left to take the ramp toward Apollo Bch.
Turn left onto Big Bend Rd.
Turn left onto S US Highway 41/US-41 S/FL-45.
Turn slight right onto Miller Mac Rd.
Welcome to APOLLO BEACH, FL.
